										<p>At the University of Lodz there is a <strong>Mobility Coordinator</strong> at&nbsp;each faculty. Such person&nbsp;is responsible for contact with partner universities (e.g. signing agreements) and taking care of mobility students. To view list of Mobility Coordinators, please follow the link below and choose faculty of your interest:</p>
