								<div class="textmedia-item textmedia-text">
									<h2 class="section-header "> NOMINATION OF MOBILITY STUDENTS </h2>
									<div class="text-regular">
										<p>Dear colleagues from partner universities, please know that nomination deadlines are as follows:</p>
										<ul class="list-normal">
											<li>winter semester/full year: 24 April</li>
											<li>summer semester: 24 October</li>
										</ul>
										<p>To nominate your students, please send an email to <a href="mailto:iso@uni.lodz.pl">iso@uni.lodz.pl</a>&nbsp;</p>
