										<div class="card-body">
											<ol>
												<li>The official inauguration of the academic year takes place on 1 October 2025.</li>
												<li>Inauguration of the academic year at the Faculties should take place until 1 October 2025.</li>
												<li>Didactic classes start on 2 October 2025 and last until 25 January 2026.</li>
												<li>Days off from the didactic classes are, as follows:
													<ul>
