													</ul>
												</li>
												<li>Examination sessions in the winter semester take place on the following dates:
													<ul>
														<li>from 26 January&nbsp;to 8&nbsp;February 2026 ‚Äì winter examination session;</li>
														<li>from 16 to 22&nbsp;February&nbsp;2026 ‚Äì winter make-up examination session.</li>
													</ul>
												</li>
