												<li>Didactic classes start on 23 February&nbsp;and last until 14&nbsp;June 2026.</li>
												<li>Days off from the classes are, as follows:
													<ul>
														<li>from 1 to 7&nbsp;April 2026&nbsp;‚Äì Easter holiday break;</li>
														<li>2 May 2025 ‚Äì Rector‚Äôs day;</li>
														<li>one May Friday ‚Äì might be declared the Rector‚Äôs day due to Juwenalia (students' festival);</li>
